数据字典

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

定义：
url                 varchar(512)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

admin_table                 管理员用户表
ID
username       varchar(32)
password       varchar(32)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

banner_table                焦点图表
ID
title           varchar(32)
description     varchar(255)
href            varchar(512)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

intro_table                 产品介绍表
ID
title           varchar(32)
description     varchar(255)
href            varchar(512)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

custom_evaluation_table     用户评价表
ID
title           varchar(32)
description     varchar(255)
src             varchar(512)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

news_table                  新闻表
ID
title           varchar(128)
summary         varchar(512)
ico_src         varchar(512)
big_pic_src     varchar(512)
content         text

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

blog_table                  博文表
ID
title            varchar(128)
pic_src          varchar(512)
big_pic_src      varchar(512)
summary          varchar(512)
content          text
post_time        timestamp
author           varchar(32)
n_view           int


---------------------------------------------------------------------------

contact_table               地址表
ID
street          varchar(64)
phone           varchar(16)
fax             varchar(16)
email           varchar(64)
weibo           varchar(64)
wechat          varchar(64)
map             ?

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

msg_table                   发送信息表
ID
name            varchar(32)
email           varchar(64)
phone           varchar(16)
subject         text

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

aboutus_table               关于我们表
ID
title          varchar(255)
content        text
pic_src        varchar(512)
href           varchar(512)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
